  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your cataplana to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Roll out the puff pastry and cut into diamond shapes.",
    "In a pan, heat 1 tbsp of coconut oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the lardons and cook until crispy, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add the turmeric, garam masala, cumin, coriander, and red chili powder. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the myeongnan-roe and cook until warmed through, about 2 minutes.",
    "Place a diamond-shaped puff pastry piece in the cataplana, then spoon the myeongnan-roe mixture on top.",
    "Fold the puff pastry over the filling, pressing gently to seal.",
    "Brush the tops with coconut oil and bake for 12-15 minutes, or until golden brown.",
    "Garnish with chopped cilantro and serve immediately."
  ],
